  "synopsis": "Ye Feng, a genius in alchemy, was ambushed and transported 500 years into the future as he attempted to break through the shackles of heaven and earth. Seeking revenge, Ye Feng embarks on the path of cultivation anew, diligently honing his skills while exploring the mysteries of the heavenly Dao. With his astonishing efforts and talent, he becomes renowned throughout the Nine Provinces, traversing the heavens. Thus begins a legendary tale of a passionate and ruthless evil emperor.\n\n(Source: Youku, translated)",
